quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,121,"Ne olwa warula mumabwibwi nolekha Abandu bobo, shichila okhupanga Abasuubili muliyie, ne Nyasaye awuulilanga ne amanyile muno"
  3,122,"Emikanda chibili mwinywe nichinjilamwo oburi, mbu betsa okhushilwa, ne Nyasaye niye omulindi wabu, Ne Abasuubili besikesa Nyasaye yenyene"
  3,123,Ne Nyasaye yabahabina mubadiri nanyu nimuli abateshele. Kho murie Nyasaye kho munyoole okhupa orio
  3,124,Olwa waboolela Abasuubili mbu; ‘’koo shibibayela tawe nikali mbu Nyasaye wenyu alabakhoonya nende Abamalaika elfu tsitaru abeshibwa (okhurula mwikulu)?’’
  3,125,"Koo, nimwista okhuba abesumilisi mana murie Nyasaye nekata Abasuku nibabarusia mapwoka, awo Nyasaye wenyu omulesi alabakhoonya nende Abamalaika elfu tsirano batsunukhanga nibalwana namaani"
  3,126,"Ne Nyasaye shiyakhola kano halali bube obusangali khwinywe, ne emioyo chenyu chinyoole okhwihotselesia, ne obukhoonyi shiburulanga awundi tawe halali khu Nyasaye, Owoluyali Owamani Owamachesi"
  3,127,"Endio nilwokhuba atete ebuleka khubakhayi nohomba abaresie banyoole okhukalukha inyuma, nabo nibatorere"
  3,128,"Na ewe obula liosiliosi mukano, nalabaleshela nohomba abahelesie eshinyasio shichilabo ni abamabii"
  3,129,"Nebiosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo ni bia Nyasaye, aleshelanga wayenya ne ahelesinjia wayenya eshinyasio, ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno Owetsimbabaasi"